{"tid":1425663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[齊齊投訴]推到林作仆街","createTime":"2019-08-06T19:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:55:27.000Z","uid":159582,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fac694a3e966541c2af3c071d2faa900bf1b8e68","tid":1425663,"uid":159582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:25:47.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知大家有冇睇到林作個FB Post: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jolamchok/posts/2136307199812627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjolamchok%2Fposts%2F2136307199812627&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=948bd63c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jolamchok/posts/2136307199812627</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://snag.gy/lsMWT5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsnag.gy%2FlsMWT5.jpg&h=6618e3c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鬧前線食彈既記者本身已經過份<br />\n<img src=\"https://snag.gy/nI5KPm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsnag.gy%2FnI5KPm.jpg&h=5a06e345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲要人身攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://snag.gy/CBxqFT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsnag.gy%2FCBxqFT.jpg&h=f8935974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又英式幽默呀?<br />\n<img src=\"https://snag.gy/rku0bH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsnag.gy%2Frku0bH.jpg&h=e9015ae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死雞撐完飯蓋鬧人pussy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://snag.gy/8xq7Y9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsnag.gy%2F8xq7Y9.jpg&h=8bce359e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n野就唔多講啦，一齊投訴到佢冇得o係燈塔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n踐踏前線記者尊嚴 鳩嗡得你咁開心呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31f186353707bcb2532ec2d482fc587a9b98e87","tid":1425663,"uid":159582,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:26:22.000Z","msg":"封信o喺度:<br />\n<br />\n致有關人士：<br />\n<br />\n近日貴公司的導師林作先生於Facebook發佈帖子，表達他對記者的個人意見。然而，他的措詞粗鄙，先回應稱留言者為「a weak person」，然後認為對方「suck so much」、稱其他辯駁者為「pussy」。確有網民的言詞尖酸刻薄。然而，林作先生以自以為的英式幽默妨害他人名譽、對人冷嘲熱諷，不僅枉為人師，更稱不上是合格的社會公民。<br />\n<br />\n據聞以往遵理學校有老師因捲入桃色醜聞而遭停職處分，讓我確信貴校不會允許人格敗壞的人執教鞭，故我中學時有五年，都有報讀貴校的補習課程；人格卑下的人，沒有資格當老師。附上林作的Facebook截圖（截自<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jolamchok/posts/2136307199812627），特此函達。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjolamchok%2Fposts%2F2136307199812627%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%AD%A4%E5%87%BD%E9%81%94%E3%80%82&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=43c85180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/jolamchok/posts/2136307199812627），特此函達。</a>"},{"pid":"79239e05e864500bc1ca652de41ebb71904a336a","tid":1425663,"uid":159582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:26:56.000Z","msg":"改返下款同報讀年數就ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af798cfceb7c686f5a057077026b362c6a0c46a","tid":1425663,"uid":159582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:27:45.000Z","msg":"[投訴林作網上言論粗鄙]<br />\nsend左去關公部:cs@beacon.com.hk<br />\n另外cc左去general個email到 :beacon@beacon.com.hk"},{"pid":"d18e833e7f081a64cef04cb7358dc91678f23c4c","tid":1425663,"uid":159582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:28:15.000Z","msg":"正一小丑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7929a83048facb59b23a5ab205cc772f3146ad2","tid":1425663,"uid":159